<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.2.3">
<l>pāviyal vētanaṉ mālai palakoṇṭu</l>
<l>tēvarkaṇ māmuṉi variṟaiñ caniṉṟa</l>
<l>cēvaṭi mēlaṇi cempoṟ ṟuḻāyeṉṟē</l>
<l>kūvumāl kōḷviṉai yāṭṭiyēṉ kōtaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“The red golden Tulsi [that is the] decoration on the red feet</l>
<l>to which gods [and] great sages constantly bow,</l>
<l>taking many [verses] from the good garland of the versified Vedas”,</l>
<l>crows the garland of me [who is] a women of murderous deeds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
